{"tid":2116884,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"直啪花生醬真係享受","createTime":"2020-07-20T12:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T08:40:19.000Z","uid":126044,"like":38,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"0b8afe3bbd31cea78ec5aec9d546640a8a44c032","tid":2116884,"uid":126044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:29:37.000Z","msg":"食開直啪真係返唔到轉頭<br />\n出街食醬多,薄薄一浸花生醬到喉唔到肺<br />\n<br />\n好多人話肥<br />\n唔好講話肥, 有得直啪花生醬短幾年命都制<br />\n<br />\n我食哂呢隻, 無添加<br />\n<img src=\"https://cf.shopee.tw/file/f1360630821c2e4f73f8c7bbd55088f9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcf.shopee.tw%2Ffile%2Ff1360630821c2e4f73f8c7bbd55088f9&h=c2a5c92d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bcd30a5b3f4e37ecfbaf969fa5380f96b2588543","tid":2116884,"uid":126044,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:39:32.000Z","msg":"雖然我唔係為左健康先食花生醬<br />\n健唔健康我都係照食<br />\n<br />\n但都要平反一下<br />\n其實花生醬冇一般大眾睇得咁差<br />\n只要識揀冇加植物油同糖<br />\n&gt;80%不飽和脂, 唔會升高壞膽固醇<br />\n<br />\n熱量係高, 食得多一定容易肥<br />\n但對比起好多零食(芝士, 奶茶, cake)佢唔見得特別差"},{"pid":"4245343314ae7aac5beb04e6af649557bc95e96b","tid":2116884,"uid":59481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:40:40.000Z","msg":"天然既花生醬好健康,相對黎講會貴D<br />\n你呢隻我之前買過黎食,勁好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf6dc7f88a2706d776301e14d3609b622c955a7","tid":2116884,"uid":138217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:41:56.000Z","msg":"樓主個隻邊到有得買"},{"pid":"ccdee18956002fd20ac19a92b3af49670f00ffa1","tid":2116884,"uid":3063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4245343314ae7aac5beb04e6af649557bc95e96b","tid":2116884,"uid":59481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:40:40.000Z","msg":"天然既花生醬好健康,相對黎講會貴D<br />\n你呢隻我之前買過黎食,勁好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:43:05.000Z","msg":"非洲係派花生醬去解決兒童營養問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e12a2d45b100d4a581c57ed39f0cfec557eb5a1","tid":2116884,"uid":126044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bf6dc7f88a2706d776301e14d3609b622c955a7","tid":2116884,"uid":138217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:41:56.000Z","msg":"樓主個隻邊到有得買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:43:53.000Z","msg":"百佳都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb74d8e62cfa4c55169d65452632c564c827469","tid":2116884,"uid":126044,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4245343314ae7aac5beb04e6af649557bc95e96b","tid":2116884,"uid":59481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:40:40.000Z","msg":"天然既花生醬好健康,相對黎講會貴D<br />\n你呢隻我之前買過黎食,勁好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:56:22.000Z","msg":"呢隻算係性價比OK<br />\n<br />\n我曾經係market place/citysuper 貨架踎過加加埋埋有一兩粒鍾<br />\n每樽花生醬拎上手睇過哂D ingredient list<br />\n<br />\n貴野唔一定無添加<br />\n&gt; $60, 玻璃樽個D 一樣有機會加D palm oil, 糖, 植物油同埋一D chem major 先識既化學野<br />\n貴可能只係貴在佢係進口貨, 或者有機, 但唔保証健康同好食"},{"pid":"7a363d36a4fec277d9536e9d920c41e2e5bf06de","tid":2116884,"uid":349976,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:57:43.000Z","msg":"直啪Nutella 仲正。"},{"pid":"b794935f6a2c4cddceccf98366e6751616317157","tid":2116884,"uid":126044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7a363d36a4fec277d9536e9d920c41e2e5bf06de","tid":2116884,"uid":349976,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:57:43.000Z","msg":"直啪Nutella 仲正。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T13:07:56.000Z","msg":"識貨<br />\n文字上真係好難解釋到直啪個種滿足感<br />\n<br />\n槳住個嘴既口感+罪惡感<br />\n一大湯